title: The Cafe-Bar at Gloucester Guild Hall
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Beer/Wine, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Predominantly vegetarian cafe situated in a bar within the Gloucester Guildhall concert venue. Relaxed atmosphere and range of vegan choices. Fully traceable food and coffee. Full bar, including local beers. Occasionally serves fish. Food from 12-2:30pm.
